518
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:37,180
Idemanda ang aming hotel?

519
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,790
Seryoso ba yun?

520
00:22:44,790 --> 00:22:45,510
Noon,

521
00:22:45,510 --> 00:22:46,790
nang imbitahan ko si Qiao Feifei na manatili

522
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:48,400
sa aming Purong Hotel,

523
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:50,510
Naghintay ako sa labas ng pinto ng manager niya,
walang pagkain o inumin,

524
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:51,590
